            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大    深股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後升幅擴大，深股升逾1%重上15000關，兩市成交合計     億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日升21點或0.52%，報4016，今早以4074點開市，跌10點或0.25%，早段見4074，跌11點或0.26%，為全日低位，隨即反覆向上，午後升破上午高，最高見4102，升17點或0.41%，為全日高位，全日成交10936.26 億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日報15177，升195點或1.3%，今早開市報14897點，亦跌84點或0.56%，已為全日低位，午後節節向上，最高見15170，升188點或1.25%，全日成交14661.59億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日升31點或0.66%，今早開跌16點或0.35%，開報4751點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日升63點或1.73%，報3752點，今早開市報3660點，跌28點或0.77%。</p>\n</div>",
